                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>Detroit</placeName>\n                <date>Novemb 13/51</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Philad.</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Your favor of the <date>28th</date> ult and also<lb/> your\n                    <sic>valueable</sic> magazine came to hand<lb/> We enclose $3 for our\n                subscription &amp; $3 for<lb/>\n                <persName>C &amp; C E Baessler</persName>\n                <placeName>Detroit</placeName> to whose address<lb/> you will also please to send\n                the Occident</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">We shall when an opportunity<lb/> offers gladly speak to our friends\n                of the<lb/> Occident &amp; your translated bible &amp; solicit<lb/>\n                subscription.</p>\n            <p>As regards our congregation here, it counts<lb/> only a very limited number of\n                members<lb/> &amp; is of a quite recent organization.<lb/> Several men having moved\n                here with their<lb/>\n                <del>their</del> families (sometime last year) the<lb/> total want of all\n                opportunities for religious<lb/> instruction of their children was severely<lb/>\n                felt especially as their business called<lb/> them away from home most of the\n                time.<lb/> Subsequently at a meeting called among<lb/> those few <add>Hebrew</add>\n                residing here (12 members)<lb/> it was resolved to call a teacher &amp; shochet<lb/>\n                &amp; also to buy a plot of land for a <sic>burrying</sic><lb/> ground. The incident\n                expenses though con,<lb/>siderable were contributed with a good<lb/> deal of\n                liberality &amp; the above resolution carved out.<lb/> The number of our member has\n                since then<lb/> augmented to 18.</p>\n            <p>The prospects for erection of a synagogue are<lb/> rather remote yet being so few in\n                number<lb/> it will have to be differed to a <sic>latter</sic></p>\n            "
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3b85443n/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
