                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "\n            <p>and more auspicious period.<lb/> Should on your contemplated western tour<lb/> you\n                happen to visit <placeName>Detroit</placeName> allow us<lb/> to invite you to call\n                on us.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">We shall cheerfully <sic>attent</sic> to any thing that<lb/> might\n                be of service to your cause.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Wishing you health &amp; happiness</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">We remain Respectfully</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">\n                <persName>S Freedman &amp; Bros</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">by <persName role=\"author\">Joseph Freedman</persName></p>\n            "
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3b85443n/canvas/p2"
